      "rationale": "The CFD solver (OpenFOAM v9) and neural network training code are maintained in a Git repository with tagged releases. Python environment is pinned via a requirements.txt manifest. Unit tests cover data preprocessing and loss computation. Achieved level exceeds MRL 2 requirement."
