      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Statistical characterization of test sample variability (hematocrit, blood age, donor variability).",
      "rationale": "Not assessed at MRL 2. Three independent blood batches were used across experimental sessions; inter-batch variability was not formally characterized. This is acceptable at MRL 2 given that model influence is Medium and experimental data serve a confirmatory rather than primary role."
